comments: Bates-Diop (SAS) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Carter (PHX) makes clean hand on ball contact as he tries to steal the ball from Bates-Diop (SAS).
Vassell's (SAS) foot remains in bounds upon receiving the pass and starting his dribble.
Galloway (PHX) legally contests Weatherspoon's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Eubanks (SAS) has his hands resting on Smith's (PHX) back and releases from the contact as he pursues the long rebound.
Eubanks (SAS) makes hand on ball contact to cleanly deflect away the post entry pass to Smith (PHX).

Carter (PHX) makes clean ball contact to dislodge it from Eubanks (SAS) in the post. Any contact between them or with Craig (PHX) as they go to the ground to pursue the loose ball is deemed incidental.
Eubanks (SAS) retracts his arm into a vertical position and marginal contact occurs with Moore's (PHX) arm, which does not affect his intended pass.
Craig (PHX) makes contact with Jones' (SAS) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Craig (PHX) tries to secure the rebound with two hands and marginal contact occurs to Bates-Diop's (SAS) arm after the release on his tip-in.
Jones (SAS) commits a take foul on Moore (PHX).
Jones (SAS) legally contests Moore's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Craig (PHX) legally contests and cleanly blocks Vassell's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
